result.name: Ying Kee Noodle

reviews.text: Place is crowded, noodle is tasty but there is only 1 kind of noodle there, no other choice.
Great place and Food
One of the best late night supper in kowloon. Large or small, chicken wings, veggies, and drinks . That's the menu and it rocks !!!

I have been auntie's customer since 1985 when I was 3. She started selling the same noodles with a small street booth in front of McDonald's in tai kok tsui. Their quality is always the same at a high level.
Delicious! Better than I expected. Got the small bowl of noodles, 4 chicken wings, and vegetables. $60 HKD
